@prefix shapes: <https://github.com/International-Data-Spaces-Association/InformationModel/master/examples/contract-and-usage-policy/templates/> .


shapes:DurationOfferTemplateShape
    a sh:NodeShape ;
    sh:targetClass ids:DurationOffer ;
    sh:node shapes:HasProviderOrConsumerNodeShape ;
    sh:property shapes:DurationOfferTemplate-permissionPropertyShape ;
    sh:message "<https://raw.githubusercontent.com/International-Data-Spaces-Association/InformationModel/master/examples/contract-and-usage-policy/templates/TimeRestrictedUsageTemplates/DurationOfferTemplateShape.ttl> (DurationOfferTemplateShape): In a _:DurationOffer a) the ids:provider property must point to one participant or b) the ids:consumer property must point to one participant or c) the ids:provider and the ids:consumer must point to one participant. This can in any case be a) an IRI or b) an ids:Participant. The ids:permission property must point to at exactly one ids:Permission. In the ids:Permission the ids:target and ids:action properties and at least one of (ids:assigner or ids:assignee) pointing to a participant have to be specified. The ids:constraint property must point to an ids:Constraint with ids:leftOperand idsc:ELAPSED_TIME, ids:operator idsc:SHORTER_EQ and ids:rightOperand pointing xsd:duration specifying the duration of the agreement."@en ;
.


shapes:DurationOfferTemplate-permissionPropertyShape
    a sh:PropertyShape ;
    sh:path ids:permission ;
    sh:class ids:Permission ;
    sh:node shapes:DurationOfferPermissionTemplate ;
    sh:minCount 1 ;
    sh:maxCount 1 ;
    sh:severity sh:Violation ;
    sh:message "<https://raw.githubusercontent.com/International-Data-Spaces-Association/InformationModel/master/examples/contract-and-usage-policy/templates/TimeRestrictedUsageTemplates/DurationOfferTemplateShape.ttl> (DurationOfferTemplate-permissionPropertyShape): In a _:DurationOffer the ids:permission property must point to at exactly one ids:Permission. In the ids:Permission the ids:target and ids:action properties and at least one of (ids:assigner or ids:assignee) pointing to a participant have to be specified. The ids:constraint property must point to an ids:Constraint with ids:leftOperand idsc:ELAPSED_TIME, ids:operator idsc:SHORTER_EQ and ids:rightOperand pointing xsd:duration specifying the duration of the agreement."@en ;
.


shapes:DurationOfferPermissionTemplate
    a sh:NodeShape ;
    sh:node shapes:HasAssignerOrAssigneeNodeShape ;
    sh:property shapes:PermissionTemplate-targetPropertyShape ;
    sh:property shapes:PermissionTemplate-actionPropertyShape ;
    sh:property shapes:DurationPermissionTemplate-constraintPropertyShape ;
.
